text: Just small pizzas here instead of slices you find in the mall.  Pizza was just okay.  The lady helping us was friendly.  This is located in the food court post security.

text: Very disappointing but one of only 5 options in Jacksonville airport. Essentially flavorless, calorie dense bread. They were out of salads too so the only option was pitiful personal pizza, Stromboli, or breadsticks.
